{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875794324,"sessionID":"ses_2858f6ed1ffeJK9Yu7VH3Ei7mv","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7225710012ESIgLJiNn2pmU","messageID":"msg_d7a72115c001YzCCtbaLCoGpr5","sessionID":"ses_2858f6ed1ffeJK9Yu7VH3Ei7mv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-941a34c2aff8449e87bd28d5c248406b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-024 ŌĆö DockerService Õ░üĶŻģ\n2: \n3: **Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n4: **Language:** Python  \n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Overview\n10: \n11: [TO BE FILLED: Overview of DockerService encapsulation]\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n16: \n17: ### Requirement: [TO BE FILLED]\n18: \n19: [TO BE FILLED: Describe scenarios]\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## Constants Summary\n24: \n25: | Constant | Value | File | Purpose |\n26: |----------|-------|------|---------|\n27: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n28: \n29: ---\n30: \n31: ## Dependencies Summary\n32: \n33: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n34: |---------|---------|---------|\n35: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## File Changes Summary\n40: \n41: | File | Action | Description |\n42: |------|--------|-------------|\n43: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ## References\n48: \n49: - [TO BE FILLED: Add relevant references]\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## Validation Checklist\n54: \n55: - [ ] [TO BE FILLED]\n\n(End of file - total 55 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-024 ŌĆö DockerService Õ░üĶŻģ\n\n**Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Overview of DockerService encapsulation]\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: [TO BE FILLED]\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Describe scenarios]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775875794308,"end":1775875794321}}}}
